column5: Remarkably accurate flavor of fruity cereal over creamy milk it has a complex-yet-immediately-familiar taste that flawlessly balances the crispness of a newly-opened box of fruity cereal with the rich indulgent flavor of fresh milk.
A delicious flavor of delectable strawberry red vines. A perfect depiction of Red Vine Licorice!

The Milkman has taken a warm toasted fruit tart thrown it into a blender with a dollop of delicious vanilla bean ice cream and a splash of fresh milk delivering a truly sensational flavor right to your taste buds in a delicious vapable 99% VG bottle.
Classic tres leches cake with a fruity glaze
Orange pineapple upside-down cake with brown sugar glaze
A slice of creamy Flan Napolitano
Creamy grape mamba milkshake
Blueberry Shortbread cookies with a creamy lemon frosting
A creamy raspberry tart
Snake Bite will bite you harder than a starvin rattler with its blend of anise citrus and jackfruit.
The good Doctors take on vanilla custard blends a creamy custard with notes of honey and rose with eye-popping results.
This tea aint for sissies.  It starts off smooth with a steeped ginger tea and strawberry blend then catches you by surprise with an amaretto kick on the finish.

Our practice has made Claim Your Throne perfect. Enjoy a blend of sweet creams butterscotch and brown sugar. Theres nothing else like it anywhere. So dont take the plunge unless youre ready for something unique.

This is it: the e-liquid that will capture your attention and keep it forever. Sweet custard. Spice. Ripened stone fruits. Its a twist on traditional fruit flavors. When the crown calls you will answer.

When you aim high you can achieve wonders. And The King is the juice that towers above all else. Its a sophisticated liquid birthed from imagination and dedication perfectly balanced and infused with mysterious flavors.

Your day is what you make of it. And Fight Your Fate is the juice to take with you on your journey. This beautifully crafted liquid will wrap you in tart lemons and sweet ripe-ripe strawberries. It all combines to create the experience you dream of.
Smooth creamy peanut butter with banana cream and balanced with velvety caramel. Buttery and smooth with a medium bodied throat hit
Intense complexity of Irish cream cinnamon spice and caramel with subtle absinthe undertones.  Lively and with a medium to full bodied throat hit.
Sweet and mellow ripe apple with savory pie crust and caramel. Topped off with French Vanilla ice cream and unsweetened whipped cream. Sweet and savory with a medium bodied throat hit.
Crisp mint with subtle chocolate undertones and a French vanilla finish. Delicate yet soft with a refreshing tingle and medium to full bodied throat hit
Delicate blood orange with creamy French vanilla.  Light yet creamy citrus with a medium bodied throat hit.

Our non-barreled aged version is a combination of the dark refined spirit ofKentucky Bourbon accented with toasted coconut roasted almond Madagascar vanilla bean and laced with a caramelized brown sugar.

Also capturing characteristics of dark spirits is our spiced rum mixed with a juicy clingstone white peach creating the flavor harmony of a fruit cobbler with a savory reduction sauce garnished by freshly shaved hazelnut.

This is the first of our flavors that utilizes a clear grapefruit liqueur with a dark refined cognac. This light and refreshing blend is reminiscent of a chilled mojito hybrid. Weve combined cucumber lemon zest and muddled mint with just a hint of dill.

This lively blend is reminiscent of the lost vintage drink known as the \“Lime Rickey\” but with a sweet champagne substitute. The effervescent note of horehound herb is counterbalanced by a sweet cream vanilla bean and a hint of roasted almond with a twist of lime.
Our tart unique blackcurrant liqueur makes this delicate blend of citrus lemon sweet fig and barley with a cinnamon stick finish complete for a warm and inviting edition.

Castle Long Reserve has been aged and steeped in a treated oak barrel for three weeks youll taste toasted coconut roasted almond brown sugar two different vanillas (Madagascar vanilla bean and French vanilla) Kentucky bourbon and charred oak
Decaf double espresso infused with black truffle cream.
Caramelized banana atop buttermilk pancakes.
A rich vanilla cream with hints for fudge and notes of cinnamon.
A tropical blueberry Popsicle that will knock your pants off.
A floral citrus blend reminiscent of mimosas.
A spiritual experience of peanut butter and jelly.
Farm fresh strawberry\'s homemade ice cream.
Pineapple upside down pancake with a blackberry maple drizzle.
Spineberry is like one of those tropical drinks you get on the beach in the Caribbean that frosts your tongue with a sweet flavor of strawberry and pineapple.
The Last Stand which is a creamy and sweet (but not overly rich) vanilla custard with a smooth inhale and an indulgent sweet vanilla exhale!  This one is SURE to please the masses!
Go buy yourself a bag of gummy bears take a handful and start chewing. Relive your youth with this sugary treat that you will never ever forget.
Just like Mom used to make for the holidays! Tart apples with caramel and spice wrapped up in a sweet and sugary crust.
Its like strolling into your neighborhood candy store! Fresh grape and strawberry coated with sugary sweetness. This flavor is developing a serious following.
Creamy pudding loaded with freshly picked strawberries and banana.
Pineapples passion fruit and a mixed medley of other tropical goodies blend perfectly with a chilled fruit juice cocktail to create a relaxing paradise-invoking e-liquid experience.
Perfectly balances sweet fresh-sliced peaches with rich orgasmic cream much to the delight of drippers everywhere.
An espresso-soaked Italian cake layered with whipped creamy deliciousness.
Magically-melded mishmash of mixed berries and laces them with a euphoric strawberry glaze to create a most trippy equine experience.
Golden graham crackers squished in cocoa kisses and marshmallow clouds.

Want to go to exotic places? Sucker Punch from Suicide Bunny is your ticket. Enjoy the alluring dragon fruit mix laced with a silky-smooth cream. And get transported to a whole new world of amazing flavor.
Rich and creamy the O.B. from Suicide Bunny gives you a new experience every time. Theres layers upon layers to savor. What kind of taste will you discover?

Ahh the enchantment of Madrina. This is Pip the Bunnys personal favorite. Try it and youll see why. It might be the enchanting cream base. It might be the notes of melon tucked into every layer. It might be all of the above and more. Try it and taste for yourself.

Welcome to Derailed: one of Suicide Bunnys most popular flavors. Inhale for the fresh baked cookie taste exhale for the sweet cinnamon banana and enjoy every moment in between. The smell alone will keep you coming back for more.

Welcome to Mothers Milk: Suicide Bunnys most popular juice. With a deliciously rich and creamy dessert flavor and a light strawberry exhale Mothers Milk is ready to rock your world. Theres a reason our fans have voted it their favorite: once you try it youll never want another.
A honey graham cracker cerel a handful of toasted nuts and a freshly sliced banana then pours creamy milk over top of it.
Balances mango cantaloupe and papaya perfectly creating a smooth not-too-sweet mouthwatering tropical medley.
A bakery cinnamon with sweet milky cream to create a very all-day-vapable e-juice that will hit those breakfast cereal notes your taste buds crave.
Its like a blend of four different cream flavors mixed with all natural strawberry extract.
Strawberry Milk With Cream
Cap n Rex which models its flavor profile after Cap n Crunchs Crunch Berry cereal. This is a delicious all day vape you will enjoy.
Troop Loops brings you a smooth milk flavor on the inhale bathed over a sugary fruit flavored exhale that tastes just like delicious fruit loops cereal.
A refreshing blend of apples strawberries and fresh juicy peaches.
Smooth creamy sophisticated and delicious.  Eclipse blends a cavendish tobacco with vanilla notes that will make your taste buds dance.
Sweet ripe strawberries coat your mouth with deliciousness followed by crisp bubbly champagne that bursts through on the exhale.
The taste of fresh picked peaches with just a hint of vanilla cream dance in your mouth with this juice thats crafted using real natural peach flavoring.
Starship 1 starts with a rich smooth vanilla custard then tops it with fresh kiwi and a touch of sweetness.
Venus is a delicious blend of campfire-roasted marshmallows smothered with peanut butter and caramel then topped with a touch of sweet cream.
Anxiety is a frosty winter breeze on inhale and a fiery burn on exhale. This will have you anxious for more.
Like rising out of bed from a bad dream to sending you jumping out of your seat this fiery cinnamon will bring your taste buds to the edge.

Feeling nostalgic? This milky fruity vape will defiinitely take you back to your saturday morning cartoon days. The Hype is Real... The flavor that changed the industry and made its own category \"The Cereal Vape\"!!!
A Warm Sweet Cinnamon French Toast Smothered in Maple Syrup
Smooth creamy yogurt infused with strawberries.
Spot-on Greek yogurt topped off with fresh blueberries.
The perfect blend of peanut butter flavored frozen yogurt and crushed hazelnuts neither of which are overpowering and will keep you coming back for more.
Fresh pineapple extract is blended with rich smooth sweet cream to create a vape experience thats akin to eating a mouthful of pineapple whip.
If youre lucky you might hit the jackpot and win a bottle of this gem a warm apple pie served up as it should be à la mode.
A simple light apple cider perfect for an all day.
A vanilla bean yogurt infused with pear.
An intense red licorice reminiscent of childhood red vines.
A sweet strawberry merged into a crisp green apple and hints of apricot. Watermelon and Eastern spices finish off this amazing flavor.
A zesty lemony inhale softened by a creamy perpetually changing and complex exhale which leads to a flavor reminiscent of a freshly baked lemon pie.
A touch of caramel united with hints of pie crush tangerine and freshly baked vanilla cake yield an expertly blended and delicately mastered dessert flavor.
Lively blend of strawberries and raspberries that give way to a tart lemony finish.

A perfect parfait of fresh raspberries give way to a smooth vanilla yogurt encased in a cinnamon crumble finish. Hints of granola appear throughout the inhale resulting in an inventive flavor profile.
A succulent and lively blend of lemon and fresh berries. Pronounced strawberry interlaces with a fresh bright and revitalizing raspberry quickly transforming into a rush of fresh lemon.
A strong and juicy watermelon. On the inhale it gives way to a sugary and luscious bubble gum finishing in a perfect balance of harmoniously layered perfection.
A full-bodied buttery blend of baked crust almonds delicate caramel Tahitian vanilla fresh cream and a touch of peanut butter. Beautifully rounded out with two types of exotic custards.
Consists of gooey sugar cookie overtones that give way to subtle hints of cinnamon sugar. Delicately blended with a hint or fresh lemon.
A perfectly balanced yet explosive tangerine twisted with subtle and exotic creams. A touch of sweetness rounds this flavor out in a way that separates it from the crowd.
Hints of the classic cocktail garnished with notes of ripe raspberries sweet oranges and a hint of lemon zest.
An indulgent freshly baked strawberry short cake shrouded in fresh whipped cream with bright top notes of custard finished with sweet cream and drizzled with a touch of fresh strawberry.
Hand-picked mountain grown Gaviota strawberries blended with just enough soft creamy Greek yogurt
Love is in the air with a refreshing trifecta of papaya orange and guava. Sweet and delicious its truly a perfect fusion of flavor you will fall in love with.
Only the best of both worlds. The Sinner combines two kinds of cooling mint with smooth robust tobacco for a wickedly exquisite mix of flavor unlike anything youve experienced before.
A playful twist of sweet orange blended with two kinds of luscious cream and a hint of vanilla. Tangy creamy and delicious The Joker is sure to put a smile on your face.

Fresh juicy and sweet to taste. Thats what you will find in our newest addition to our lineup. Miami Ice is a fruity peach schnapps cocktail over ice designed to satisfy your cravings any time of day.

We\'ve tipped our hand and in your favor. By combining creamy milk chocolate with subtle tones of spiced rum we have created a blend that will satisfy even the most extreme chocolate craving as well as give it a little zing to entice your taste buds.
With an ingenious mixture of vanilla orange cream and sweet milky notes Broadway is sure to please even the most sophisticated pallet.
